"38c3bb34-61ad-800b-9893-ed25d148dac7" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">JSON 또는 XML 형식의 문서와 같은 반정형 데이터를 저장하도록 설계 됨</li></ul></div></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-80b1-bbb5-cfc5a34bed73" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">그래프 데이터베이스<div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-805a-a5db-daefa8ff55e4" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">간선이라고 부르는 방향 링크와 정점을 저장</li></ul></div></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-8054-80cf-fa001833a8d9" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">인 메모리 키-값 스토어<div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-804e-8266-dead8a7071dc" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">인 메모리 캐싱은 핵심 데이터 조각을 메모리에 저장해 액세스 지연 시간을 줄여주므로애플리케이션 성능이 향상 됨</li></ul></div></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><h2 id="38c3bb34-61ad-804d-8774-cbc0e57231ea" class="">2. DynamoDB</h2></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><hr id="38c3bb34-61ad-8041-b377-c3de8d0b57ad"/></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><div id="38c3bb34-61ad-806a-afcf-e29f27fb9c20" class="column-list"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><div id="38c3bb34-61ad-8013-8298-d848f49b662b" style="width:106.25%" class="column"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-804b-ba5d-c0c302524b9a" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc"><mark class="highlight-pink"><strong>완전관리형 클라우드 NoSQL 데이터베이스</strong></mark><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-80a3-bc02-c601472a9af5" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">규모와 관계없이 10ms 미만의 지연 시간 보장</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-80ab-9acc-d1977e8db266" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">유연한 데이터 모델, 용량 제한 없음</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-8061-b600-e69d9252d869" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">안정적인 성능</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-80c7-85ed-c89d4f9e2d2f" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">처리 용량 자동 조정 기능</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-8021-84ef-e3e9793f4b20" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">용량과 읽기/쓰기 유닛에 대하여 과금</li></ul></div></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-8037-bffb-f442e783352b" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc"><mark class="highlight-pink"><strong>Amazon DynamoDB Accelerator (DAX)</strong></mark><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-80f6-b88a-f3dbc938300b" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">가용성이 뛰어난 완전관리형 인 메모리 캐시</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-8018-aaba-d859f00c7cb0" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">초당 수백만 개의 요청에도 DynamoDB 응답 시간을밀리초에서 마이크로초로 단축할 수 있음</li></ul></div></li></ul></div></div></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><div id="38c3bb34-61ad-80e8-b3df-e3400a913642" style="width:43.74999999999998%" class="column"><div style="display:contents" dir="ltr"><figure id="38c3bb34-61ad-80b4-ad28-e9ca69bc18f7" class="image"><img style="width:132px" src="https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/8743bb34-61ad-813e-a746-000390a09a4b/7f8ad4af-2024-4f39-8cfc-c193bf1eba73/image.png?X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Content-Sha256=UNSIGNED-PAYLOAD&amp;X-Amz-Credential=ASIAZI2LB466UFPABK7E%2F20260630%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260630T235554Z&amp;X-Amz-Expires=21600&amp;X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjEAYaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJIMEYCIQDMK5owQdpiT8Qq5iSgeNxJDWd4rU6dq5%2BcQIJXI6uC1wIhAOoa8HQG%2F9JQkPfC%2Ff1zMghVG37cAYIQUqptMLIgaZbmKogECM7%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2FwEQABoMNjM3NDIzMTgzODA1Igyssu5ee5RE0ptIhLsq3AMOONehfBgYVd0y2YqYFoVM02aGQpuJ5XzfK4sNuKefq8KDT7J2t%2BqLHQV1PxV9vkdcg3KWLq51NzKtxtlIb6t6hdPmQARUWS3iZOHV8JiE7IZlBArw%2BwSu8XfWoZJXw2ijKVl3Sj8GEzIfpfRi%2F9kbKXccMKRd3fAwjr%2B7QmSk64c0EPYbpHiuCARzabHcNelapA5%2F4401%2BdLXNfLV1J6eL0v7AxPVwSp6BIx2yVoqlMyFNagJSEn%2BJp1utIabklG2MgfV6CKue0DfM7kGC0p%2Bek75p7%2FrHV1mIQYusGi9jkuDrKqTv0m6vEtX7LpXnkobn8TAj2dFyIkv2YrwG8va%2BkS9vv5z%2BbXCgIlGxrqjXl4M46Y7aYJDfOzs%2F6KRATbfk1QtpskAFQkd%2FlZ9YP9mewCDWEJoVjFJQbsTLiQ8P7wR025M4wJEjk0HckTYZKrxY2wh879h%2BWH01X7cQVMBtgwv1Brts28MMJbv%2BJXlv%2Fa87pPJid6T1mOJMxyL2pXT4sZ04zy2kJhcddYnq1OF0NrvSZcoZx%2FTu9f7RRsqqCAM17JxF%2BiJ9YAifIWJZhQwHQ3Fwd7qoP7xeXt7wNKX3rdK7YPRMe%2BegDndgJgxqALAQcXRIwE%2FgAzX1zDQ6JDSBjqkAf4EL73981AnB5o8TXIRoF36dI6P8BfOjBGBSICn9y0w8Vftna5UGHI3zmU1oDfZDzejfg37yJgT2%2BzaWzZpOWtA87bAlaTvQ%2B7%2Br7Ez4T9MwvhDrgUfdUfUZPP1PgzMFgaW1DVbcA1oPDVFPAoiSHoi%2BtYq9hBB%2FaMD%2BjGCCwuJNpNk6kyZacjgZ%2BUjhIajsr5paDNSl1Bm8ItMGe1w4tAyAXOd&amp;X-Amz-Signature=8f75fb3846bcbb454b372ec4aa845dabcac95d28130225206ac59d58e62f707c&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;x-amz-checksum-mode=ENABLED&amp;x-id=GetObject"/></figure></div></div></div></div></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><h3 id="38c3bb34-61ad-80a2-adc4-fc9d9a43c07e" class="">DynamoDB Read 방식</h3></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-80ba-a119-ee06a558c128" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc"><mark class="highlight-pink"><strong>Eventually Consistent Read</strong></mark>  ⬅︎  <em><mark class="highlight-red">따로 지정하지 않으면 기본으로 사용됨</mark></em><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-80ee-b69f-d6b313ab2a72" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">최근 완료된 쓰기 작업의 결과를 반영하지 않을 수 있음</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-80a8-ad7a-e830609b3822" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">부실 데이터가 일부 포함될 수 있음</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-8083-b709-c38e1ecc0869" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">잠시 후 읽기 요청을 반복하면 응답이 최신 데이터를 반환</li></ul></div></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-806c-9706-f85abdca7242" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc"><mark class="highlight-pink"><strong>Strongly Consistent Read</strong></mark><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-8079-b926-c00e7da6e6b2" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">성공한 모든 이전 쓰기 작업의 업데이트를 반영하여, 가장 최신 데이터로 응답을 반환</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-80a6-bbf7-c382c04ea66e" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">네트워크 지연 또는 중단이 발생한 경우에 사용이 어려울 수 있음</li></ul></div></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><h3 id="38c3bb34-61ad-8004-8182-df7afc608917" class="">DynamoDB 과금 방식</h3></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-80ef-a99f-e88d220b0a33" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">데이터 스토리지 <div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-80bd-9deb-e75b730487c0" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">테이블에서 사용한 디스크 공간(GB)당 시간당 요금을 부과</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-80b8-b2f1-df6bdcaa9dcc" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">GB당 월 0.27 USD</li></ul></div></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-800a-a4b1-d5425fb3234f" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">읽기 용량 유닛<div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-80ab-a139-e89a849fae9a" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">1 읽기 용량 유닛 = 초당 최대 2건의 읽기 작업을 제공 (월별 5백 2십만 건)</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-804d-8382-d0c4f77c6edc" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">읽기 요청 유닛 100만 건당 0.271 USD</li></ul></div></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-80a0-b488-d1174912d9f9" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">쓰기 용량 유닛<div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-80d1-9114-e452c67b9224" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">1 쓰기 용량 유닛 = 초당 최대 1건의 쓰기 작업을 제공 (월별 2백 6십만 건)</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-8066-be73-da79ecfdab2c" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">쓰기 요청 유닛 100만 건당 1.3556 USD</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="38c3bb34-61ad-8070-9fc8-fa26152af855" class=""><a href="https://aws.amazon.com/ko/dynamodb/pricing/">https://aws.amazon.com/ko/dynamodb/pricing/</a></p></div></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><h3 id="38c3bb34-61ad-8040-83bc-f8fbf9c7b9ef" class="">DynamoDB 기본 구성</h3></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><div id="38c3bb34-61ad-80a4-aa98-c2fc69a72e16" class="column-list"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><div id="38c3bb34-61ad-8067-8dd9-c2f31b0416b2" style="width:68.75%" class="column"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-80c3-81de-de15b6c81879" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">Table<div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-8088-a780-e598aefd67fb" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">Item들의 집합</li></ul></div></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-80b6-8e4c-c8b3f44f28ab" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">Item<div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-80c0-b8a6-c402544bf198" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">Attribute들의 집합</li></ul></div></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-80dd-947f-f2f9577bc5d5" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">Attribute<div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-807c-8345-e80b8321084b" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">Key-Value방식의 데이터</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-8014-8b0a-dbf405ca0941" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">Key는 문자열</li></ul></div></li></ul></div></div></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><div id="38c3bb34-61ad-8059-ae1a-cfe7e8cd413f" style="width:106.25%" class="column"><div style="display:contents" dir="ltr"><figure id="38c3bb34-61ad-8026-80f7-d229942b6681" class="image"><img style="width:2164px" src="https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/8743bb34-61ad-813e-a746-000390a09a4b/a45fd9f8-386f-4437-be1b-88511f765f46/image.png?X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Content-Sha256=UNSIGNED-PAYLOAD&amp;X-Amz-Credential=ASIAZI2LB466UFPABK7E%2F20260630%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260630T235554Z&amp;X-Amz-Expires=21600&amp;X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjEAYaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJIMEYCIQDMK5owQdpiT8Qq5iSgeNxJDWd4rU6dq5%2BcQIJXI6uC1wIhAOoa8HQG%2F9JQkPfC%2Ff1zMghVG37cAYIQUqptMLIgaZbmKogECM7%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2FwEQABoMNjM3NDIzMTgzODA1Igyssu5ee5RE0ptIhLsq3AMOONehfBgYVd0y2YqYFoVM02aGQpuJ5XzfK4sNuKefq8KDT7J2t%2BqLHQV1PxV9vkdcg3KWLq51NzKtxtlIb6t6hdPmQARUWS3iZOHV8JiE7IZlBArw%2BwSu8XfWoZJXw2ijKVl3Sj8GEzIfpfRi%2F9kbKXccMKRd3fAwjr%2B7QmSk64c0EPYbpHiuCARzabHcNelapA5%2F4401%2BdLXNfLV1J6eL0v7AxPVwSp6BIx2yVoqlMyFNagJSEn%2BJp1utIabklG2MgfV6CKue0DfM7kGC0p%2Bek75p7%2FrHV1mIQYusGi9jkuDrKqTv0m6vEtX7LpXnkobn8TAj2dFyIkv2YrwG8va%2BkS9vv5z%2BbXCgIlGxrqjXl4M46Y7aYJDfOzs%2F6KRATbfk1QtpskAFQkd%2FlZ9YP9mewCDWEJoVjFJQbsTLiQ8P7wR025M4wJEjk0HckTYZKrxY2wh879h%2BWH01X7cQVMBtgwv1Brts28MMJbv%2BJXlv%2Fa87pPJid6T1mOJMxyL2pXT4sZ04zy2kJhcddYnq1OF0NrvSZcoZx%2FTu9f7RRsqqCAM17JxF%2BiJ9YAifIWJZhQwHQ3Fwd7qoP7xeXt7wNKX3rdK7YPRMe%2BegDndgJgxqALAQcXRIwE%2FgAzX1zDQ6JDSBjqkAf4EL73981AnB5o8TXIRoF36dI6P8BfOjBGBSICn9y0w8Vftna5UGHI3zmU1oDfZDzejfg37yJgT2%2BzaWzZpOWtA87bAlaTvQ%2B7%2Br7Ez4T9MwvhDrgUfdUfUZPP1PgzMFgaW1DVbcA1oPDVFPAoiSHoi%2BtYq9hBB%2FaMD%2BjGCCwuJNpNk6kyZacjgZ%2BUjhIajsr5paDNSl1Bm8ItMGe1w4tAyAXOd&amp;X-Amz-Signature=5b44f7514676cc18c879133e4d3cdc014b0123047033933e7cb6c421de99610c&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;x-amz-checksum-mode=ENABLED&amp;x-id=GetObject"/></figure></div></div></div></div></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="38c3bb34-61ad-801b-919d-eae74247f666" class="">
</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="38c3bb34-61ad-807a-9e6d-ff094996f5bd" class="">
</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><h2 id="38c3bb34-61ad-8051-9d2a-eeb8e10182f1" class="">3. DynamoDB 데이터 타입</h2></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><hr id="38c3bb34-61ad-8096-b846-e2fff329aa31"/></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-8092-9ca0-e0f052b25047" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">참고 <a href="https://docs.aws.amazon.com/ko_kr/amazondynamodb/latest/developerguide/HowItWorks.NamingRulesDataTypes.html">ttps://docs.aws.amazon.com/ko_kr/amazondynamodb/latest/developerguide/HowItWorks.NamingRulesDataTypes.html</a></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-8057-bf90-d0b041e569e1" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">DynamoDB 스칼라 데이터 형식 (하나의 값만 표현)<div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-8094-94a6-d71149f35436" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">Number (N) : 양수, 음수 또는 0. 최대 38자리까지 지원.</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-80fa-a436-d13554735922" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">String (S) : UTF-8 이진 인코딩 을 사용하는 유니코드.</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-8009-a8bf-d4e003aaaea0" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">Binary (B) : 압축 텍스트, 암호화 데이터, 또는 이미지 같은 모든 이진수 데이터 저장 가능.</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-8065-91d4-d0d3817c953f" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">Boolean (S, “0” 또는 “1”) : true 또는false 를 저장할 수 있음.</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-8070-a870-ff95acf74f75" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">Null (NULL) : 알려지지 않았거나 정의되지 않은 상태의 속성.</li></ul></div></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-8074-ad1a-f86f971a17c2" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">DynamoDB 문서 형식(내포 속성이 있는 복잡한 구조를 표현)<div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-808f-9f03-ff5f8d63be42" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">List (L) : 순서가 지정된 값 모음을 저장할 수 있음.</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-805f-aee1-c81607f02733" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">Map (M) : 정렬되지 않은 이름-값 쌍의 모음을 저장할 수 있음.</li></ul></div></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-8025-a83c-c9329a3f0818" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">DynamoDB 다중 값 형식<div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-8020-9b03-c12d6e288016" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">다중 값 형식 (여러 스칼라 값을 표현)</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-807d-a1f2-ef44f9256db6" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">String Set (SS) : 문자열 집합</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-8037-8a60-d73d4c0203f8" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">Number Set (NS) : 숫자 집합</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-8079-8b82-db64a277a52f" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">Binary Set (BS) : 이진 집합</li></ul></div></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><h2 id="38c3bb34-61ad-8009-88f0-d72890b9d7a9" class="">4. DynamoDB 파티션 및 키</h2></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><hr id="38c3bb34-61ad-8024-af3b-c7c1f79ad6f2"/></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-8081-8c4d-f3031bdee31f" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc"><strong>DynamoDB 파티션</strong><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-807e-8b7d-c80e569c21d7" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle"><mark class="highlight-pink"><strong>파티션 (Partition) : </strong></mark><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-80eb-8705-e2f2c3e3dd35" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:square"><span style="border-bottom:0.05em solid">DynamoDB가 데이터를 저장하는 곳</span></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-805a-8385-f9a59e8bb164" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:square">SSD(Solid State Drive)로 백업되는 테이블용 스토리지 할당</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-80f2-b7bc-fb76f03fbec9" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:square">하나의 AWS 리전 내의 여러 가용 영역에 자동으로 복제됨</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-80cc-b770-d70da7940693" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:square">직접 관리할 필요 없이 파티션 관리는 전적으로 DynamoDB에서 처리 함</li></ul></div></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-80fa-9e11-c4787da34dd0" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle"><mark class="highlight-pink"><strong>다음과 같은 상황에 테이블에 추가 파티션을 할당</strong></mark><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-8051-8463-d58add8af881" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:square">기존 파티션이 지원할 수 있는 <strong>한도를 초과</strong>하여, 테이블의 할당된 처리량 설정을 늘리는경우</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-8043-971f-efe471c8b932" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:square">기존 파티션 용량이 다 차서 <strong>추가 스토리지 공간이 필요</strong>한 경우</li></ul></div></li></ul></div></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-80cf-a8df-d5c6e0a4d88d" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc"><strong>DynamoDB 키</strong><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-8055-9a95-f68a6e4971fa" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle"><mark class="highlight-pink"><strong>기본 키 (Primary Key)</strong></mark><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-806e-b0a8-e90a94b22961" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:square">Table내에서 각 Item을 구분하는 고유 식별자</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-807f-b69f-eba93f568615" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:square">단순 기본 키: 파티션 키만 사용</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-809f-9771-cdc771de4ea4" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:square">복합 기본 키: 파티션 키와 정렬 키를 함께 사용</li></ul></div></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-80bf-b8dd-e863c344242e" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle"><mark class="highlight-pink"><strong>파티션 키 (Partition Key)</strong></mark><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-8039-9f67-f773d718f390" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:square">내부 해시 함수에 대한 입력으로 파티션 키 값을 사용</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-8015-bb61-f83d80d325ea" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:square">출력에 따라 항목을 저장할 파티션이 결정됨</li></ul></div></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-8039-8b32-ddabf1b5915f" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle"><mark class="highlight-pink"><strong>정렬 키 (Sort Key)</strong></mark><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-805b-bcb8-f3972afc8183" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:square">파티션 키가 동일한 모든 항목들을 정렬하는 키 값</li></ul></div></li></ul></div></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="ltr"><figure id="38c3bb34-61ad-8008-a84b-c9f045242475" class="image"><img style="width:576px" src="https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/8743bb34-61ad-813e-a746-000390a09a4b/502d9f62-9848-4fe1-95b4-02eb72f28f8f/image.png?X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Content-Sha256=UNSIGNED-PAYLOAD&amp;X-Amz-Credential=ASIAZI2LB466UFPABK7E%2F20260630%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260630T235554Z&amp;X-Amz-Expires=21600&amp;X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjEAYaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJIME