</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-8092-ba26-fa1f8705fdbd" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">먼저 파티션 키를 해시 함수의 입력으로 전달하여 Item이 저장되어 있는 파티션을 찾고, 이후에 해당 파티션 내에서 정렬 키를 사용하여 Item을 찾게 됩니다</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><h2 id="38c3bb34-61ad-80cb-9b3d-def5a47123ca" class="">5. DynamoDB 보조 인덱스</h2></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><hr id="38c3bb34-61ad-80a3-8472-fef3d8ab65eb"/></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-80dc-8ac9-d0acadccdea3" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">하나 이상의 보조 인덱스를 생성할 수 있음, 보조 인덱스는 파티션 키에 대한 쿼리는 물론이고, 정렬 키를 사용하여 테이블 데이터에 대한 쿼리까지 실행</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-80dd-aab0-c5d44735de4a" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">DynamoDB 보조 인덱스<div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-80ee-bccc-deac3745fbe9" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle"><mark class="highlight-pink"><strong>로컬 보조 인덱스 (Local Secondary Index, LSI)</strong></mark><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-80ae-86c0-e5ceb78faef0" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:square">테이블과 파티션 키는 동일하지만 정렬 키는 다른 인덱스</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-8031-a062-f313830794ef" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:square">정렬 키(Sort Key)를 추가로 더 만든다고 생각하면 됨!</li></ul></div></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-807f-bf3c-eb6c8bc75242" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle"><mark class="highlight-pink"><strong>글로벌 보조 인덱스 (Global Secondary Index, GSI)</strong></mark><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-80d7-9a00-f4f38648a6e3" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:square">파티션 키 및 정렬 키가 테이블의 파티션 키 및 정렬 키와 다를 수 있는 인덱스</li></ul></div></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-8024-8169-df27188be701" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle"><mark class="highlight-pink"><strong>보조 인덱스 개수 제한</strong></mark><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-80a7-ac55-c9d1604c205e" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:square">테이블당 최대 20개의 GSI 및 5개의 LSI를 정의할 수 있음 (일부 리전 제외)</li></ul></div></li></ul></div></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="ltr"><figure id="38c3bb34-61ad-8089-91ee-d98e30c7dac5" class="image"><img style="width:5120px" src="https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/8743bb34-61ad-813e-a746-000390a09a4b/69bb40ff-9999-4d55-be5e-de61d1b6d68c/image.png?X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Content-Sha256=UNSIGNED-PAYLOAD&amp;X-Amz-Credential=ASIAZI2LB466UFPABK7E%2F20260630%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260630T235554Z&amp;X-Amz-Expires=21600&amp;X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjEAYaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJIMEYCIQDMK5owQdpiT8Qq5iSgeNxJDWd4rU6dq5%2BcQIJXI6uC1wIhAOoa8HQG%2F9JQkPfC%2Ff1zMghVG37cAYIQUqptMLIgaZbmKogECM7%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2FwEQABoMNjM3NDIzMTgzODA1Igyssu5ee5RE0ptIhLsq3AMOONehfBgYVd0y2YqYFoVM02aGQpuJ5XzfK4sNuKefq8KDT7J2t%2BqLHQV1PxV9vkdcg3KWLq51NzKtxtlIb6t6hdPmQARUWS3iZOHV8JiE7IZlBArw%2BwSu8XfWoZJXw2ijKVl3Sj8GEzIfpfRi%2F9kbKXccMKRd3fAwjr%2B7QmSk64c0EPYbpHiuCARzabHcNelapA5%2F4401%2BdLXNfLV1J6eL0v7AxPVwSp6BIx2yVoqlMyFNagJSEn%2BJp1utIabklG2MgfV6CKue0DfM7kGC0p%2Bek75p7%2FrHV1mIQYusGi9jkuDrKqTv0m6vEtX7LpXnkobn8TAj2dFyIkv2YrwG8va%2BkS9vv5z%2BbXCgIlGxrqjXl4M46Y7aYJDfOzs%2F6KRATbfk1QtpskAFQkd%2FlZ9YP9mewCDWEJoVjFJQbsTLiQ8P7wR025M4wJEjk0HckTYZKrxY2wh879h%2BWH01X7cQVMBtgwv1Brts28MMJbv%2BJXlv%2Fa87pPJid6T1mOJMxyL2pXT4sZ04zy2kJhcddYnq1OF0NrvSZcoZx%2FTu9f7RRsqqCAM17JxF%2BiJ9YAifIWJZhQwHQ3Fwd7qoP7xeXt7wNKX3rdK7YPRMe%2BegDndgJgxqALAQcXRIwE%2FgAzX1zDQ6JDSBjqkAf4EL73981AnB5o8TXIRoF36dI6P8BfOjBGBSICn9y0w8Vftna5UGHI3zmU1oDfZDzejfg37yJgT2%2BzaWzZpOWtA87bAlaTvQ%2B7%2Br7Ez4T9MwvhDrgUfdUfUZPP1PgzMFgaW1DVbcA1oPDVFPAoiSHoi%2BtYq9hBB%2FaMD%2BjGCCwuJNpNk6kyZacjgZ%2BUjhIajsr5paDNSl1Bm8ItMGe1w4tAyAXOd&amp;X-Amz-Signature=b39d873f3eea013d4bcee796c12d5579ccb03def23d50213675aa1cc90a7c5d3&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;x-amz-checksum-mode=ENABLED&amp;x-id=GetObject"/></figure></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="38c3bb34-61ad-8068-92b3-e404623453c1" class="">
</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="38c3bb34-61ad-8052-8da6-cd2dcdac2a0e" class="">
</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="ltr"><figure id="38c3bb34-61ad-807d-bbf7-f19f645a1827" class="image"><img style="width:3640px" src="https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/8743bb34-61ad-813e-a746-000390a09a4b/8b7f39a2-886f-44a9-b8b7-2671473f59cf/image.png?X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Content-Sha256=UNSIGNED-PAYLOAD&amp;X-Amz-Credential=ASIAZI2LB466UFPABK7E%2F20260630%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260630T235554Z&amp;X-Amz-Expires=21600&amp;X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjEAYaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJIMEYCIQDMK5owQdpiT8Qq5iSgeNxJDWd4rU6dq5%2BcQIJXI6uC1wIhAOoa8HQG%2F9JQkPfC%2Ff1zMghVG37cAYIQUqptMLIgaZbmKogECM7%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2FwEQABoMNjM3NDIzMTgzODA1Igyssu5ee5RE0ptIhLsq3AMOONehfBgYVd0y2YqYFoVM02aGQpuJ5XzfK4sNuKefq8KDT7J2t%2BqLHQV1PxV9vkdcg3KWLq51NzKtxtlIb6t6hdPmQARUWS3iZOHV8JiE7IZlBArw%2BwSu8XfWoZJXw2ijKVl3Sj8GEzIfpfRi%2F9kbKXccMKRd3fAwjr%2B7QmSk64c0EPYbpHiuCARzabHcNelapA5%2F4401%2BdLXNfLV1J6eL0v7AxPVwSp6BIx2yVoqlMyFNagJSEn%2BJp1utIabklG2MgfV6CKue0DfM7kGC0p%2Bek75p7%2FrHV1mIQYusGi9jkuDrKqTv0m6vEtX7LpXnkobn8TAj2dFyIkv2YrwG8va%2BkS9vv5z%2BbXCgIlGxrqjXl4M46Y7aYJDfOzs%2F6KRATbfk1QtpskAFQkd%2FlZ9YP9mewCDWEJoVjFJQbsTLiQ8P7wR025M4wJEjk0HckTYZKrxY2wh879h%2BWH01X7cQVMBtgwv1Brts28MMJbv%2BJXlv%2Fa87pPJid6T1mOJMxyL2pXT4sZ04zy2kJhcddYnq1OF0NrvSZcoZx%2FTu9f7RRsqqCAM17JxF%2BiJ9YAifIWJZhQwHQ3Fwd7qoP7xeXt7wNKX3rdK7YPRMe%2BegDndgJgxqALAQcXRIwE%2FgAzX1zDQ6JDSBjqkAf4EL73981AnB5o8TXIRoF36dI6P8BfOjBGBSICn9y0w8Vftna5UGHI3zmU1oDfZDzejfg37yJgT2%2BzaWzZpOWtA87bAlaTvQ%2B7%2Br7Ez4T9MwvhDrgUfdUfUZPP1PgzMFgaW1DVbcA1oPDVFPAoiSHoi%2BtYq9hBB%2FaMD%2BjGCCwuJNpNk6kyZacjgZ%2BUjhIajsr5paDNSl1Bm8ItMGe1w4tAyAXOd&amp;X-Amz-Signature=a3079cd1632e945f35787e120560173255df57bf20db949dbad6bdd2107b6bba&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;x-amz-checksum-mode=ENABLED&amp;x-id=GetObject"/></figure></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-8018-9588-e7b16dab055d" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc"> 테이블의 파티션 키는 Name이고 정렬 키는 Subject입니다</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-804b-af80-fbbf96c6741d" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">로컬 보조 인덱스는 테이블과 파티션 키는 동일하지만 정렬 키는 다른 인덱스</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-807f-87fa-f8c2fdea1685" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">로컬 보조 인덱스의 파티션 키는 Name으로 테이블과 동일하며, 정렬 키는 Score로 테이블과 다른 </li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-808b-9967-d629f08784bc" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">로컬 보조 인덱스를 만들어서 사용하게 되면 → Name과 Score 값을 이용해서 테이블 내에서 아이템을 찾을 수 있음</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="ltr"><figure id="38c3bb34-61ad-8010-8e9e-e86a4123b60b" class="image"><img style="width:3696px" src="https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/8743bb34-61ad-813e-a746-000390a09a4b/4ae7ed78-79be-418b-87bf-3e44d1cff7ef/image.png?X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Content-Sha256=UNSIGNED-PAYLOAD&amp;X-Amz-Credential=ASIAZI2LB466UFPABK7E%2F20260630%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260630T235554Z&amp;X-Amz-Expires=21600&amp;X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjEAYaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJIMEYCIQDMK5owQdpiT8Qq5iSgeNxJDWd4rU6dq5%2BcQIJXI6uC1wIhAOoa8HQG%2F9JQkPfC%2Ff1zMghVG37cAYIQUqptMLIgaZbmKogECM7%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2FwEQABoMNjM3NDIzMTgzODA1Igyssu5ee5RE0ptIhLsq3AMOONehfBgYVd0y2YqYFoVM02aGQpuJ5XzfK4sNuKefq8KDT7J2t%2BqLHQV1PxV9vkdcg3KWLq51NzKtxtlIb6t6hdPmQARUWS3iZOHV8JiE7IZlBArw%2BwSu8XfWoZJXw2ijKVl3Sj8GEzIfpfRi%2F9kbKXccMKRd3fAwjr%2B7QmSk64c0EPYbpHiuCARzabHcNelapA5%2F4401%2BdLXNfLV1J6eL0v7AxPVwSp6BIx2yVoqlMyFNagJSEn%2BJp1utIabklG2MgfV6CKue0DfM7kGC0p%2Bek75p7%2FrHV1mIQYusGi9jkuDrKqTv0m6vEtX7LpXnkobn8TAj2dFyIkv2YrwG8va%2BkS9vv5z%2BbXCgIlGxrqjXl4M46Y7aYJDfOzs%2F6KRATbfk1QtpskAFQkd%2FlZ9YP9mewCDWEJoVjFJQbsTLiQ8P7wR025M4wJEjk0HckTYZKrxY2wh879h%2BWH01X7cQVMBtgwv1Brts28MMJbv%2BJXlv%2Fa87pPJid6T1mOJMxyL2pXT4sZ04zy2kJhcddYnq1OF0NrvSZcoZx%2FTu9f7RRsqqCAM17JxF%2BiJ9YAifIWJZhQwHQ3Fwd7qoP7xeXt7wNKX3rdK7YPRMe%2BegDndgJgxqALAQcXRIwE%2FgAzX1zDQ6JDSBjqkAf4EL73981AnB5o8TXIRoF36dI6P8BfOjBGBSICn9y0w8Vftna5UGHI3zmU1oDfZDzejfg37yJgT2%2BzaWzZpOWtA87bAlaTvQ%2B7%2Br7Ez4T9MwvhDrgUfdUfUZPP1PgzMFgaW1DVbcA1oPDVFPAoiSHoi%2BtYq9hBB%2FaMD%2BjGCCwuJNpNk6kyZacjgZ%2BUjhIajsr5paDNSl1Bm8ItMGe1w4tAyAXOd&amp;X-Amz-Signature=8260a9c814598561fd7254ab4d08dc548f2ef3c159e2223c8e67e59009ee3865&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;x-amz-checksum-mode=ENABLED&amp;x-id=GetObject"/></figure></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-8023-b70c-e51b1762c4ca" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">파티션 키 및 정렬 키가 테이블의 파티션 키 및 정렬 키와 다를 수 있는 인덱스</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-80a6-ad94-d20b9b24b684" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">글로벌 보조 인덱스의 파티션 키는 Subject가 되고, 정렬 키는 Name</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-8041-87b1-edc0de3fda67" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">다른 값으로 파티션을 나눌 수 있고, 해당 파티션 내에서 아이템들을 정렬 할수 있음.</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="38c3bb34-61ad-805d-a033-c2a6f9494cd6" class="">
</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><h2 id="38c3bb34-61ad-80de-8e2d-d3b18bf71f91" class="">6. DynamoDB 데이터 조회</h2></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><hr id="38c3bb34-61ad-8073-8abc-c0d7b3004889"/></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-809a-908e-f335892bd3be" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc"><a href="https://docs.aws.amazon.com/ko_kr/amazondynamodb/latest/developerguide/Query.html">https://docs.aws.amazon.com/ko_kr/amazondynamodb/latest/developerguide/Query.html</a></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-800f-9133-e88571a61d56" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc"><a href="https://docs.aws.amazon.com/ko_kr/amazondynamodb/latest/developerguide/Scan.html">https://docs.aws.amazon.com/ko_kr/amazondynamodb/latest/developerguide/Scan.html</a></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="38c3bb34-61ad-802b-808f-f48317ccdf09" class="">
</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-8053-965c-e2532c918b31" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">DynamoDB의 데이터 조회 방식에는 크게 <strong>Query</strong>와 <strong>Scan</strong></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-8046-8612-c37cfb3aa684" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc"><mark class="highlight-pink"><strong>DynamoDB Query</strong></mark><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-80ae-aa51-caffad48ce6e" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">기본 키 값을 기반으로 항목을 찾음</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-8005-9d50-ed78c38792c5" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">복합 기본 키(파티션 키 및 정렬 키)가 있는 테이블 또는 보조 인덱스를 쿼리할 수 있음</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-8017-a604-db7fee047ad7" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">파티션 키 속성의 이름과 해당 속성의 단일 값을 제공해야 함</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-8032-893b-d63daf352fa6" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">해당 파티션 키 값을 갖는 모든 항목을 반환</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-806c-a57b-c74d0667cff8" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">선택적으로 정렬 키 속성을 제공하고, 비교 연산자를 사용하여 검색 결과의 범위를 좁힐 수있음</li></ul></div></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-803e-85b8-eff899917312" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc"><mark class="highlight-pink"><strong>DynamoDB Scan</strong></mark><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-8034-bea6-eda64eed6ed5" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">테이블 또는 보조 인덱스의 모든 항목을 읽어옴</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-80b1-8314-edb64a952ba1" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">기본적으로 테이블이나 인덱스에 속한 항목의 데이터 속성을 모두 반환</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-8076-a369-e3bb8a28eb51" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">ProjectionExpression 파라미터를 사용하면 일부 속성만 가져올 수 있음</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-806f-a9da-c301905095e5" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">Scan은 항상 결과 집합을 반환함<br/>(일치하는 항목이 없다면 비어있는 결과 집합이 반환 됨)</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-805a-bb1d-efed3ffed859" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">단일 Scan 요청은 최대 1 MB까지 데이터를 가져올 수 있음<br/>(옵션으로 필터 표현식을 적용하면 반환되는 결과의 범위를 좁힐 수 있음)</li></ul></div></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><blockquote id="38c3bb34-61ad-8090-bd0c-d6e36d0e0ad6" class=""><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="38c3bb34-61ad-8066-9782-eb65365f0c6a" class=""><em><strong>Query (키 값으로 찾는 것) : 학번으로 곧바로 부르는 것<br/>vs<br/>Scan (전체 데이터를 가져와서 필터링 하는 것) : 한 명씩 불러서 학번이 일치하는지 확인</strong></em></p></div></blockquote></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-80c8-9463-e525bcd8a53b" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">Scan은 속도도 느리고 비싸므로 웬만하면 사용하지 않는 것이 좋음</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="38c3bb34-61ad-809b-b8aa-e4fbf2ba56dc" class="">
</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><h2 id="38c3bb34-61ad-80fd-829d-eeab0fb42b6b" class="">7. 실습</h2></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><hr id="38c3bb34-61ad-8087-ba61-d4259ab1d4c5"/></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="38c3bb34-61ad-8069-9c8b-e82d965ddaeb" class="">
</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><h3 id="38c3bb34-61ad-8071-9190-cb19956433a9" class="">DynamoDB 테이블 설계</h3></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-80bb-8dc7-c52e9ba7961a" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">어떻게 설계할지 생각해보기<div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-8062-b137-c03ec3c53aab" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">전교생의 시험 점수를 DynamoDB에 넣어서 관리하려고 함</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-8014-a8f9-d0abeceb62f7" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">학생들은 저마다 고유의 학번을 갖고 있음</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-8063-bbdf-df0739ba7cd7" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">시험 과목은 영어, 과학, 수학 총 3과목</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-80a8-8040-d11996a68d8b" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">아래와 같은 데이터 조회가 가능해야 함<div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-8022-95ec-ea93717965c6" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:square">한 학생의 영어, 과학, 수학 점수를 다 가져오기</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-8017-9938-db893d4497a2" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:square">각 과목별 점수로 정렬하여 학생 목록 가져오기</li></ul></div></li></ul></div></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><div id="38c3bb34-61ad-8097-b5d4-f01ecedb966b" class="column-list"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><div id="38c3bb34-61ad-80a1-8287-e485abbc03d9" style="width:125%" class="column"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-8078-a295-f8546293f388" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">기본 키를 어떻게 구성해야 할까?<div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-800a-aa63-e2541bbcc651" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">기본 키 (Primary Key)<div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-80ca-9720-fc909172db85" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:square">단순 기본 키로 할 경우<div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-80b6-bfd2-ef1720406566" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">파티션 키: 학생의 학번</li></ul></div></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-8099-868c-c163a0bec126" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:square">복합 기본 키로 할 경우<div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-803a-99eb-da65518d6b4c" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">파티션 키: 학생의 학번</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="38c3bb34-61ad-805a-988a-f41b4599b13b" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">정렬 키: 과목명</li></ul></div></li></ul></div></li></ul></div></li></ul></div></div></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><div id="38c3bb34-61ad-80a0-9ca2-c4674d1d0a97" style="width:75%" class="column"><div style="display:contents" dir="ltr"><figure id="38c3bb34-61ad-8065-b6ac-d9b5710e7047" class="image"><img style="width:1648px" src="https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/8743bb34-61ad-813e-a746-000390a09a4b/1605b318-7051-4c69-8d3c-ef577fa29277/image.png?X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Content-Sha256=UNSIGNED-PAYLOAD&amp;X-Amz-Credential=ASIAZI2LB466UFPABK7E%2F20260630%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260630T235554Z&amp;X-Amz-Expires=21600&amp;X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjEAYaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJIMEYCIQDMK5owQdpiT8Qq5iSgeNxJDWd4rU6dq5%2BcQIJXI6uC1wIhAOoa8HQG%2F9JQkPfC%2Ff1zMghVG37cAYIQUqptMLIgaZbmKogECM7%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2FwEQABoMNjM3NDIzMTgzODA1Igyssu5ee5RE0ptIhLsq3AMOONehfBgYVd0y2YqYFoVM02aGQpuJ5XzfK4sNuKefq8KDT7J2t%2BqLHQV1PxV9vkdcg3KWLq51NzKtxtlIb6t6hdPmQARUWS3iZOHV8JiE7IZlBArw%2BwSu8XfWoZJXw2ijKVl3Sj8GEzIfpfRi%2F9kbKXccMKRd3fAwjr%2B7QmSk64c0EPYbpHiuCARzabHcNelapA5%2F4401%2BdLXNfLV1J6eL0v7AxPVwSp6BIx2yVoqlMyFNagJSEn%2BJp1utIabklG2MgfV6CKu